					Health and Safety Audit			</td>
				<td align="right" width="100%" class="buttonheading">
		<a href="index.php?view=article&amp;catid=16:health-and-safety&amp;id=64:health-and-safety-audit&amp;tmpl=component&amp;print=1&amp;layout=default&amp;page=&amp;option=com_content&amp;Itemid=150#" onclick="window.print();return false;">|&nbsp;Print&nbsp;|</a>		</td>
